<bibRefCitation author="Coppins, B. J. &amp; Kantvilas, G." box="[278,599,1859,1886]" pageId="2" pageNumber="211" pagination="35 - 48" refId="ref7270" refString="Coppins, B. J. &amp; Kantvilas, G. (2001) Four new species of Rimularia Nyl. (Agyriaceae). Bibliotheca Lichenologica 78: 35 - 48." type="journal article" year="2001">Coppins &amp; Kantvilas (2001)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
